Package: PBAT
Title: Plant Breeding Analytical Tools (Shiny Application)
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Krishnan P", "Abhijith",
           email = "abhijithkpgen@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8641-02X"))
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny application for plant breeding 
    analyses, including mating design analytics (diallel, line-by-tester, 
    partial diallel), ANOVA summaries, estimation of GCA/SCA effects, 
    BLUE/BLUP utilities, principal component analysis (PCA) with plots, 
    and exportable reports. Designed for non-programmers with a 
    point-and-click interface.
